  <h3> 6.4 For Category 4: List the  major Wildlife Conservation Audit / Assessment / verification/ Inspection Projects undertaken by applicant</h3>
  <table class="table" aria-label="Projects" id="cat4Projects">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>S. No.</th>
        <th>Name of Project</th>
